{"tid":1922030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《頭條新聞》啓播後收到3萬多宗讚賞, 6000多宗意見和投訴","createTime":"2020-03-12T10:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T10:47:40.000Z","uid":326897,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e56a49d920f180768ec519d8fd15b608e9f50988","tid":1922030,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:17:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514017-20200312.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514017-20200312.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BN5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=74a1d455\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514017-20200312.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c3771a77\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514017-20200312.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n廣播處長梁家榮向香港電台工作人員發信，表示自去年社會躁動至近月全民抗疫，香港電台像社會各界一樣，遇上前所未見的挑戰，感謝同事一直堅守崗位，盡心盡力為市民服務，這段期間收到的不少意見回饋，不論是讚賞、意見或投訴都是鞭策，砥礪廉隅，港台須精益求精，做好本份。<br />\n<br />\n梁家榮在信中提到過去三個星期，社會不同群組對《頭條新聞》内容表達關注，意見紛陳。他強調《頭條新聞》絕非新聞報告節目，内容特色是諷刺和針貶時弊，這類城中少有的劇種，借社會熱話，反映社會脈搏和讓觀眾舒氣釋懷。<br />\n<br />\n梁家榮表示，新一輯《頭條新聞》啓播後，上月1日至本月8日共收到<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3萬多宗讚賞</span></span></strong>，另有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">6000多宗意見和投訴</span></span></strong>。他說，任何節目均須不停完善，會珍視每宗回饋，每宗投訴亦會按現行機制審視處理，必須經常自省，虛心接受投訴，查找有待改善之處。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，絕對體會其他部門在過去一段日子的辛勞和難處，希望部門與部門之間互相理解，各司其職，更好服務市民。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足好野</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8403df9192bacf5606606003f143de9a33914c","tid":1922030,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d539c8abae3b373b34062afbd1cf4bfc37d52f7","tid":1922030,"uid":82815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b688deb41241f05c6f5df0edd9d910572841d0","tid":1922030,"uid":140140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:22:36.000Z","msg":"支持頭條新聞"},{"pid":"23b898c8d4e307e91225b9f3ba927b88dc4423b8","tid":1922030,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ae82320371f009eaca550e4ad4a311310df5be","tid":1922030,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1247528551140cee15a4a460d9d7d6d2d27375cc","tid":1922030,"uid":274722,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:24:12.000Z","msg":"3萬，thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18cb8a6da984253f13670a72f70b045d03a704b6","tid":1922030,"uid":111316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1247528551140cee15a4a460d9d7d6d2d27375cc","tid":1922030,"uid":274722,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:24:12.000Z","msg":"3萬，thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 